title: Start
body:
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
So I like to play a game while driving.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
What's the game?
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
I try to keep my foot still while braking...
And at the end, if my car doesn't bounce when it comes to a stop,
I win!
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
(sigh) I can't believe I chose to go on this date
on my birthday...
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
I wonder if I should tell her it's my birthday...
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
OH MY GOD! TURN LEFT!!!
<<beginQTE DialogueSwitcher QTETarget>>

title: Success
body:
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Uh... sorry about that.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Oh my God! You almost drove us to Canada!!
<<LoadNextLevel Canvas>>
